    <item>
      <title>毛里求斯将欺诈调查范围扩大至前财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/mauritius-extends-fraud-probe-to-former-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛里求斯下令当局逮捕前财政部长 Renganaden Padayachy，如果他试图离开该国，他将被捕。Renganaden Padayachy 是总理纳文钱德拉·拉姆古兰 (Navinchandra Ramgoolam) 新政府实施公共财政审计后的第二名受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/mauritius-extends-fraud-probe-to-former-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:39:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国将调查哈西娜的侄女和英国城市部长图利普·西迪克</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/bangladesh-to-probe-hasina-s-niece-uk-city-minister-tulip-siddiq</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国反洗钱机构要求提供有关英国金融部长图利普·西迪克（Tulip Siddiq）国内银行账户的信息，后者也是被罢免的总理谢赫·哈西娜（Sheikh Hasina）的侄女，这可能是开展更大范围金融调查的前兆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/bangladesh-to-probe-hasina-s-niece-uk-city-minister-tulip-siddiq</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:37:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和迪拜亿万富翁共同出资 200 亿美元建设数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-dubai-billionaire-unveil-20-billion-for-us-data-centers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布达马克集团负责人侯赛因·萨基瓦尼将投资至少 200 亿美元在美国建立新的数据中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-dubai-billionaire-unveil-20-billion-for-us-data-centers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:36:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洪都拉斯政府开始尝试重新规划公共债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/honduras-government-begins-bid-to-reprofile-public-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洪都拉斯总统卡斯特罗寻求释放资金用于投资，该国政府已开始努力“重新规划”公共债务。]]></description>
