      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 15:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因涉嫌腐败对奥尔班内阁首席部长罗根实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/us-sanctions-orban-s-cabinet-chief-rogan-for-alleged-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班的盟友唐纳德·特朗普入主白宫前几天，美国以涉嫌腐败为由对奥尔班极具影响力的内阁首席实施了制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/us-sanctions-orban-s-cabinet-chief-rogan-for-alleged-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 15:48:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管政府暂停征税，加拿大仍将实施资本利得税改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/canada-to-apply-capital-gains-tax-change-despite-government-halt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多暂停议会，但加拿大税务机关将继续适用更高的资本利得纳入税率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/canada-to-apply-capital-gains-tax-change-despite-government-halt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 15:39:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
